Seared Chicken Breast with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

30 min
$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

Description

Juicy seared chicken breast served alongside creamy garlic mashed potatoes, a comforting and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • potatoes: 4 medium
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
